{
  "stem": "3150.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So as to-- you could not walk around without it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- it-- it's either very late '41 or very early '42.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think-- I-- I-- I-- I believe it was-- it might have been in '41, because it was-- there was still no snow on the ground, and usually we get snow, well, we got snow very early there.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we-- we-- we probably had a house of-- of seven rooms, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, because-- well, it's-- and then we had a barn.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that time, we had no horses or cows, so we converted that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we-- we really slept four or five people per room, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it's-- and we were the lucky ones because we had a lot of room.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were the ones that our house was in a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't have to move by coincidence, because the people that had to move, they were lucky to just get a space to sleep.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, it's--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well first, we had to get the whole family in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So all the five sisters and their kids.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And probably-- and-- to bring them in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then we had to do my father's side of the family, so which they were four and their-- and their kids.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we-- we had some distant relatives that we packed them in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was allocated, really.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That-- that was allocated by the-- by the people that-- that ran the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "More or less yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, you-- you would said that you would have to-- you have to have so many people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Obviously, you put your relatives in there first.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But after that, you know, they just make you-- made you get the quota.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
